dct_title_s: Contrafactur des Treffens zwischen der Kanf: Spanisch und Braunschwigen Armaden ben Hochst
dct_description_sm: Author and imprint taken from notes assembled by map collector.
Depicts battle near Hochst, showing armies, roads, buildings, surrounding topography, vegetation.
Possibly appears in Bellus' Laurea austriaca, 1627.
